Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:22.60,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(4500,0)\c&H2521FF&\pos(260,350)\bord16\be110\3c&H2521FF&}大耳兽登场!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:22.60,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(4500,0)\c&H2521FF&\pos(70,150)\bord16\be110\3c&HFFFFFF&}你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:22.60,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(4500,0)\c&H2521FF&\pos(260,350)\bord16\be110\3c&HFFFFFF&}大耳兽登场!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我不是数码兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是我把你创造出来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 今天回来的真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快要吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什… 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊… 啊… 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,又捡些乱七八糟的垃圾回来是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是一定要丢掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽 上楼咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,上楼兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不要这样 基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果别人突然看到像你一样那么大的数码兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会吓死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易才和你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不想永远在一起吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我希望你可以乖乖听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗? 基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔— 兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我是启人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,启— 人—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不是启人兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是启人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,启人兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是数码兽 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我是你的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,启人兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不对啦 我是启人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的数码兽驯兽师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,探测到一只野生一号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它正在吸收周围的数据并不断增大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,启动追踪器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是追踪器的虚拟景象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙… 也要实体化吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊… 没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什… 么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,啊… 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,启人是独子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那个… 比如说… 嗯… 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不— 行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我说不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,请考虑一下我们家的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可没工夫照顾它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,明天你就郑重的告诉启人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就说家里不能养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喂— 那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是谁在烧篝火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,妖狐兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:57.05,Note,,0,0,0,,（Gobli，即Goblin，是一种丑陋的小妖精\N通译地精，亦有译为哥布林、戈柏林的）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,野人兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(317,438)}Goblimon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,成长期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼人型 病毒种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,性格缺乏勇气 却十分奸诈狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,必杀技是向对手扔火球的地精袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(473,438)}Gobli Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,数据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么来的 这个玩具 好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 喂 刚才你们俩人在干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,古乐兽想知道自己不知道的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你 一直在看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,何止是这样 这不是什么玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就走了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,数据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,留姬 选项卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
