Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,野人兽进化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.63,Note,,0,0,0,,名字来源：Fuga,也许来自于fuugai(风害)，这意味着强风的冲击造成损害。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(317,438)}Fuugamon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,库加兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,进化了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,它应该不能进化的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么特别的啊 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,数— 据—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,妖狐兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,输了绝不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 你看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,数— 据—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.04,牧野留姬,,0,0,0,,狐叶楔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你进化成成熟期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我方的参数还是比较高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你变强了哦 妖狐兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊 以前不是也捡过猫回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那才不是捡回来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是公园里的一位老婆婆送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么来的 反正你知道我们家是卖吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以绝对不可以养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道这次你又弄了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我希望你把它送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽 可以了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点窄 但你还是忍一下吧 基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去学校直到太阳落山才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不能一直和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,听好哦 你在这里等直到我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要听话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了就一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,饿了的话 就吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖地在这里直到我回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.98,Note,,0,0,0,,（Grey为Great的误写，意为伟大的\NMetal意为金属）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(224,438)}Greymon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(394,438)}MetalGreymon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,暴龙兽进化 机械暴龙兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:27.26,Note,,0,0,0,,（Were为Werewolf的缩写，意为狼人）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(403,438)}WereGarurumon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是合步进化 兽人加鲁鲁兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,高速插件B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太遗憾了 程序紧急中止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是启人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上刚好有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,干吗带了个护目镜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很酷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我成为数码兽驯兽师了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,第一节课是体育课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早起来就要跑步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我把这里收拾一下就来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,果然没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那张蓝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊 启人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,3米46
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 多了5厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还是比你多3厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为博和你比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好 那么就下个人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24}喂 山崎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你个猪头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天不是说了不要忘记写作业的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 现在是上课时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对 上课时不要分心 对对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,同学 同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪个班的学生?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽 你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,黑泽清二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我是校长 请叫我校长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,找启人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你说玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是上课的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,总之你先把这怪怪的盒子脱下来再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为启人说不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这学校里必须听我校长先生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,懂不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么一起玩吧 校长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不玩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来… 来… 来人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大家排好队在这里等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老师去看看怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 启人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我… 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了 我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它还跟我说了很多话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,校长先生不会是喝了酒才来学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样 那就成了学校的怪谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是又要给我们放假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不要出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.15,Note,,0,0,0,,（冇问题为粤语，意为没问题，即所谓莫慢待）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,冇问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,听说是怪兽 怪兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有那样的东西出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看到怪兽了所以按了消防铃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:16:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真的看见了按下去也不奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,面包全部都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁拿的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是全校学生份量的面包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 快点重新准备面包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,希望可以赶上供餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是基尔兽干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么跑来学校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才说基尔兽 是么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是数码兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人也是驯兽师吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.98,Note,,0,0,0,,（Terrier：梗犬，一类最初为打猎和消除毒蛇害虫而培育的犬种）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(321,438)}Terriermon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大耳兽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大耳兽在… 说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,管不好自己的搭档数码兽的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是不够资格当数码兽驯兽师的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大耳兽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,冇问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,启人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,启人 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:20:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,启人的脸湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在我说可以之前 你就在这里藏好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,放学之后我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就一起玩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好地方的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 启人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28}我想找一个基尔兽可以独自呆着也不会被发现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我看这一带好像很少有人出入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,基尔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让开 驯兽师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是数码兽的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？ 我好像在哪见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妖狐兽想要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,----------ED-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.72,ED,,0,0,0,,来吧  现在开始出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:18.18,ED,,0,0,0,,前往地图上没有的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:23.23,ED,,0,0,0,,那些令人恐惧的东西 没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:29.32,ED,,0,0,0,,小小的心中 充满的只有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:33.95,ED,,0,0,0,,在雨中 独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:40.87,ED,,0,0,0,,即使只有空空如也的衣袋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:46.42,ED,,0,0,0,,我也绝不回头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:53.05,ED,,0,0,0,,开启未知的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:59.01,ED,,0,0,0,,向着世界的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.92,ED,,0,0,0,,进发 进发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:05.31,ED,,0,0,0,,已经不再迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:06.94,ED,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:12.78,ED,,0,0,0,,现在开始出发 前往地图上没有的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:18.57,ED,,0,0,0,,那些令人恐惧的东西 没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:24.58,ED,,0,0,0,,把握住今天以后 才能够创造明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:32.96,ED,,0,0,0,,振翅飞翔  飞向遥远的 My Tomorrow
